title: 225: Proprioception is Hot!
description: Proprioception... the awareness of your body in space. Why is this so important, especially if your goal is to build muscle and look good? Sal, Adam & Justin give you the goods on why proprioception can help you overcome plateaus, avoid injury and build more muscle. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
